snippet.title: Eden of Ikemen: Love in a Lost World - Official Trailer // FREE Otome Game
snippet.description:
"Who will you choose to live with in an eden of love and desire?"

DEAD OR LOVE is a smash hit otome game that has gained more than 
200,000 avid fans and we present you with the direct sequel!

Eden of Ikemen: Love in a Lost World is the newest work 
by AbracadabraGames x EMIQ!

Download the game here:
✨ Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=info.otomedou.fwe.edenofikemenEn
✨ iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/eden-of-ikemen-otome/id1474048871?l=ja&ls=1
